patthana23.41:1.1_0: Nasanidassanasappaṭighaṁ navipākaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca anidassanaappaṭigho vipāko dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana23.41:2.1_0: Nasanidassanasappaṭighaṁ navipākadhammadhammaṁ paccayā anidassanaappaṭigho vipākadhammadhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana23.41:3.1_0: Nasanidassanasappaṭighaṁ nanevavipākanavipākadhammadhammaṁ paṭicca sanidassanasappaṭigho nevavipākanavipākadhammadhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
